pan></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82-%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">业务需求-建设思路</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E5%9C%B0%E5%9B%BE%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%B7%A1%E5%8C%BA%E6%88%96%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%86%E5%8C%96%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF-%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E6%8E%92%E7%8F%AD%EF%BC%8C%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E6%8C%87%E6%8C%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%A4%84%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%91%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%A4%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%8B%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%A4%E8%AD%A6%E4%BE%BF%E6%8D%B7%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%8E%E7%A1%AE%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A1%E5%8C%BA%E5%92%8C%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">总体目标为：基于电子地图实现巡区或路线的可视化、可查询、可 编辑、可排班，提高指挥中心处置效率，并支持任务信息可下发至交警手台，让交警便捷地明确自己的巡区和路线。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E5%BD%93%E6%97%A5%E5%87%BA%E5%8B%A4%E8%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E8%A7%84%E6%A8%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A1%E9%80%BB%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E3%80%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">系统可以根据当日出勤警力规模，在满足响应时间前提下，推荐合理的巡逻任务配置方案。</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-5\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%B0%86%E5%8F%98%E6%9B%B4%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E4%B8%8E%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%91%E8%87%B3%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A4%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%8B%E5%8F%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%87%BA%E5%8B%A4%E8%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6